b'In line with the decision of the Association of Banks in Lebanon, to contain Covid-19 virus, Bank Audi Lebanon branches will be closed from March 17 until March 29, 2020. The Bank is taking all necessary measures to ensure business continuity in public administrations, provide cash for withdrawal in ATMs and ITMs, process salaries, as well as all transactions of companies involved in food security, medical equipment and other sectors supported by BDL.
For your banking needs, you can use our ATM network and our digital banking channels, or call our 24/7 Contact Center on 1570 or 01/212120.
Looking forward to serving you at our branches, once this global health crisis is over. Until then, please stay safe. \xe2\x80\x8e\xd8\xa8\xd9\x86\xd8\xa7\xd8\xa1\xd9\x8b \xd9\x84\xd9\x82\xd8\xb1\xd8\xa7\xd8\xb1 \xd8\xac\xd9\x85\xd8\xb9\xd9\x8a\xd8\xa9
